description: Oboya Horticulture Industries AB engages in the development, production, and trading of agricultural products for industrial and home cultivation, and indoor environment use. The company is headquartered in Moelndal, Vastra Gotalands and currently employs 232 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2014-11-14.
